title: Miami-FSU tee it up; NW-Michigan, Cal-Utah in league games
text: > Top News Miami-FSU tee it up; NW-Michigan, Cal-Utah in league games FILE - In this Nov. 15, 2014, file photo, Miami's Michael Badgley (24) attempts a field goal in the first half an NCAA college football game against Florida State in Miami Gardens, Fla. New coaches, new players, new era, but the 'Canes (3-1) and 12th-ranked 'Noles (4-0) tee it up again on Saturday, Oct. 10, 2015, with Florida State looking to make it five wins in a row over Miami. (AP Photo/Lynne Sladky, File)
